title: Ep. 46 Ft. Royce Da 5'9
itunes:title: Ep. 46 Ft. Royce Da 5'9
description:
Right before releasing "Layers," his most introspective album to date, Royce da 5'9 kicks it with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago, Gigi Maguire and guest host Sofi Green about how alcoholism affected his marriage, being sober for almost 4 years, and not having first dates. He gives advice to the women on one thing they can do to prevent their man from cheating, why women shouldn't ever cheat, and agrees that his sex tape was subpar.
